ntion": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1647231152, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647237286, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 5, "pid": 18413, "poll": null, "reply": 5, "text": "有个问题一直想问问，炒股票不是应该投入大量的时间去研究吗？那我们普通人按理说肯定炒不过那些基金经理啊，可是为什么看起来很多人自己边上班边炒股，而且看起来炒的不比基金经理差？", "timestamp": 1647231152}, {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": null, "create_time": 1647231102, "cw": "xxg", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647237039, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 18412, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "春天到了，好想亲亲抱抱doi", "timestamp": 1647231102}, {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [], "create_time": 1647230997, "cw": "股票相关", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1647230997, "likenum": 1, "n_attentions": 1, "n_comments": 0, "pid": 18411, "poll": null, "reply": 0, "text": "#17670\n今日标题：宛如牛市\n今日操作：\nT了浙江建投，还小加了一点（收7个点以下不涨停是主力要开二波的温柔）\nT了黑牡丹，小减一点，已经盈利，被美丽云卡位难受\n新开1.5成仓ST科迪，0.5成仓金健米业（隔离吃饭预制菜逻辑）", "timestamp": 1647230997}, {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 50449, "create_time": 1647231637, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "准确的说是新冠检测会延续，但不是现在，刚刚高潮分化\n中丐只有放量才能上去，没增量资金看都不看，走出右侧抄底来得及", "timestamp": 1647231637}], "create_time": 1647230736, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time":